data.description: Beautiful new construction by Branson Homes. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath full bath, 2 car garage home features: open living plan, granite in kitchen, isolated master bedroom, wood flooring, huge utility room, sodded yards and on and on. Easy access to Georgia st, 58th and the loop. Canyon schools. All of this at an affordable price.
